y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明把口講到睇唔起窮毒撚，但係佢地最大嘅金主就係一班溝唔到女嘅窮毒撚，所以話課金到撚樣真係社會賤種地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520c1512bb4e1fb55c572aa906b7860e1816c5f3","tid":2416963,"uid":303057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:58:46.000Z","msg":"其實資本主義下<br />\n有需求自然有供應<br />\n依家屌佢哋賣相<br />\n咁市場有呢個需求呢樣嘢就會一直存在<br />\n如果無人買自然會摺埋<br />\n咁賣相出現似乎只係一個正常嘅經濟學現象<br />\n咁點解仲要屌鳩佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（賣藥嗰啲犯法你屌是可以的）<br />\n請指教"},{"pid":"e32820584a90eec414a528cd92858d14a3118be1","tid":2416963,"uid":132986,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:48:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">電子雞係公廁係垃圾係軍妓係狗<br />\n二穴闊過西隧<br />\n同明星藝人完全係兩回事<br />\n你地係雞黎架咋！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當中以屎家軍軍妓為最為娼狂<br />\n人造鹿 人造馬 蔥蔥 乃軍中公廁<br />\n只要有錢收 後庭都可以任意開發<br />\n<del>媽媽</del> 馬馬仲會call fd陪訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（流出）電子雞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2414805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2414805</a><br />\n<br />\n其實馬馬(rose ma)呢張相係咪玩緊cosplay？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2170719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2170719</a><br />\n<br />\nRose ma 做雞床照流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2169492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2169492</a><br />\n<br />\n［分享喜悅］屎家軍細b睇場既紅資cga又呃人錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2254122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2254122</a><br />\n<br />\n［打擊網絡垃圾］屎萊姆同屎炮車試水溫想復出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144946</a><br />\n<br />\n［狂賀］屎家軍夾公仔舖違反停業令 連續兩日被爆格<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136037</a><br />\n<br />\n屎家軍集中地旺角CGA電競館違反停業令<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2124475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2124475</a><br />\n<br />\n［細b知法犯法］乜紅店CGA有特權可以係武肺期間繼續營業架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2132739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2132739</a><br />\n<br />\n屎萊姆一而再再而三擺Auman上枱，Auman已經成為屎家軍既condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2076779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2076779</a><br />\n<br />\n［分享喜悅］屎萊姆你件垃圾輸唔起就唔好租台呃人錢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2091697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2091697</a><br />\n<br />\n乜而家D夾公仔鋪開鋪被人報1832兇人咁惡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2125552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2125552</a>"},{"pid":"5ce5e81df8e06d3cda1f40267d01e26f680b08ef","tid":2416963,"uid":11254,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T21:50:47.000Z","msg":"連登仔講道德<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46274ebb4bcd1cc7fb721426c7adb79008c9c72","tid":2416963,"uid":105277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"520c1512bb4e1fb55c572aa906b7860e1816c5f3","tid":2416963,"uid":303057,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T19:58:46.000Z","msg":"其實資本主義下<br />\n有需求自然有供應<br />\n依家屌佢哋賣相<br />\n咁市場有呢個需求呢樣嘢就會一直存在<br />\n如果無人買自然會摺埋<br />\n咁賣相出現似乎只係一個正常嘅經濟學現象<br />\n咁點解仲要屌鳩佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（賣藥嗰啲犯法你屌是可以的）<br />\n請指教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"藍店食肆=供<br />\n你出街食飯=求<br />\n<br />\n咁你會唔會屌? 咁你幫唔幫襯?"},{"pid":"3ecf7071278a531ee2b410f6261793aee632f9d4","tid":2416963,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0334648c6e11d7be60bb67177617dcee387cc273","tid":2416963,"uid":195271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T18:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係女人都好憎呢d 電子雞，反而有班狗公去幫呢班電子雞講說話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"你都識講係狗公<br />\n狗公一早就俾班電子雞洗哂腦"},{"pid":"1138b65224727ec4d8872695c17d02aa210b7570","tid":2416963,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite